\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Mai 15, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104iil1665702549278.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/iil1665702549278.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/iil1665702549278.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"iil1665702549278\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify the assignment file used by the application.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iil1665702549278__section_w6738ab1b5b1_w6739ab1b5_w6740ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iil1665702549278__p_d147929e1_d147930e1_d147931e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/asn=</span>{<var class=\"keyword varname\">Path</var>}<var class=\"keyword varname\">FileName</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iil1665702549278__section_w6741ab1b5b3_w6742ab1b5_w6743ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1030795e64\">\n                  \n Use With\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iil1665702549278__p_d147935e1_d147936e1_d147937e1\">All Uniface applications, including:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iil1665702549278__li_d51401e1_d51402e1_d51403e1\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">ide.exe</span> — Uniface IDE </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iil1665702549278__li_d51404e1_d51405e1_d51406e1\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">urouter</span> — Uniface Router </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iil1665702549278__li_d51407e1_d51408e1_d51409e1\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">userver</span> — Uniface Server </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iil1665702549278__li_d51410e1_d51411e1_d51412e1\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">udebug</span> — Uniface Debugger </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iil1665702549278__li_d51413e1_d51414e1_d51415e1\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">urm</span> — Uniface Resource Manager </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iil1665702549278__li_d51416e1_d51417e1_d51418e1\">User applications\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iil1665702549278__section_w6744ab1b5b5_w6745ab1b5_w6746ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1030795e110\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iil1665702549278__p_d147941e1_d147942e1_d147943e1\">Run the application using assignments from <var class=\"keyword varname\">FileName</var>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iil1665702549278__p_d147944e1_d147945e1_d147946e1\">The file specified with the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/asn</span> switch overrides both the assignment file entry for the application shell and the default assignment file, named <span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Application</var>.asn</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iil1665702549278__p_d147947e1_d147948e1_d147949e1\">If <var class=\"keyword varname\">Path</var> is omitted, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/asn</span> switch should be preceded by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/adm</span> switch to specify the location of the assignment file.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iil1665702549278__p_d147950e1_d147951e1_d147952e1\">Uniface begins by searching for a file named <var class=\"keyword varname\">FileName</var>, exactly as entered on the command line, then in lowercase characters and, finally, in uppercase. If no file is found and <var class=\"keyword varname\">FileName</var> does not contain an extension, the extension <span class=\"ph filepath\">.asn</span> is added and the search is repeated.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iil1665702549278__p_d147953e1_d147954e1_d147955e1\">If you use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/asn</span> switch to specify an assignment file with the same name as the application shell (that is, <var class=\"keyword varname\">Shell</var>\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">.asn</span>), you should be sure to include the extension <span class=\"ph filepath\">.asn</span>. Otherwise, Uniface will find the application shell <var class=\"keyword varname\">Shell</var> and try to use that as an assignment file.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iil1665702549278__section_w6747ab1b5b7_w6748ab1b5_w6749ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1030795e177\">\n                  \n Example: /asn\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iil1665702549278__p_d147959e1_d147960e1_d147961e1\">In the following example, assignments are located in a file named <span class=\"ph filepath\">another.asn</span> in the current directory:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">/asn=another</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eiq1665702549359.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>/adm</a><p>Specify the directory where the application's configuration files are located.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/exv1665702549479.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>/ini</a><p>Specify the initialization file or GUI resource file used by the application.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sjo1665702919851.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Uniface Files and Executables</a><p>During installation, a large number of files and executables are installed. Some of the most important are described in the topics in this section.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/asd1665702742243.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Configuration Files</a><p>Uniface configuration files include assignment files, initialization files, and web application files.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528563\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528563\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/asn Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Mai 15, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specify the assignment file used by the application. /asn= { Path } FileName Use With All Uniface applications, including: ide.exe — Uniface IDE urouter — Uniface Router userver — Uniface Server udebug — Uniface Debugger urm — Uniface Resource Manager User applications Description Run the application using assignments from FileName . The file specified with the /asn switch overrides both the assignment file entry for the application shell and the default assignment file, named Application .asn . If Path is omitted, the /asn switch should be preceded by the /adm switch to specify the location of the assignment file. Uniface begins by searching for a file named FileName , exactly as entered on the command line, then in lowercase characters and, finally, in uppercase. If no file is found and FileName does not contain an extension, the extension .asn is added and the search is repeated. If you use the /asn switch to specify an assignment file with the same name as the application shell (that is, Shell .asn ), you should be sure to include the extension .asn . Otherwise, Uniface will find the application shell Shell and try to use that as an assignment file. Example: /asn In the following example, assignments are located in a file named another.asn in the current directory: /asn=another Copy Related Links /adm Specify the directory where the application's configuration files are located. /ini Specify the initialization file or GUI resource file used by the application. Uniface Files and Executables During installation, a large number of files and executables are installed. Some of the most important are described in the topics in this section. Configuration Files Uniface configuration files include assignment files, initialization files, and web application files. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}